-- Basil Read to Develop Highview’s Technology, Business Day Says
-- B y   J a n i c e   K e w
-- 2012-07-11T06:44:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-11/basil-read-to-develop-highview-s-technology-business-day-says.html
Basil Read Holdings Ltd. (BSR) ’s energy
division agreed to develop London-based Highview Power Storage
Ltd.’s technology in sub-Saharan Africa, Business Day reported,
citing Highview Chief Executive Officer Gareth Brett.  Basil Read Energy will have exclusive rights to implement
Highview’s cryogenic energy storage technology in the markets in
which it operates, the Johannesburg-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Janice Kew in Johannesburg at 
 jkew4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
